<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁打开了门，魔法师走进了屋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿拉丁，我弟弟的儿子！”马格里布说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把一篮子的无花果放进了泽巴的手臂里，深深鞠了一躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后说：“弟妹，这是一点儿小小的礼物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我。”他说，“你丈夫曾经坐在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴指着墙边的垫子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我可怜的弟弟！” 马格里布大叫着跌在垫子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他看起来真的很伤心。”泽巴小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她跑向她的客人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有必要这么难过。”她说，“过来，我们吃饭吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁帮助魔法师站起来，他的妈妈拿着食物走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们坐下吃饭的时候，她开始问马格里布问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先生，为什么我之前从来没有听说过您？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我并不感到惊讶。”马格里布回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我四十年前就离开了这个小镇，我的故乡。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的丈夫那时候还是一个小男孩儿！”泽巴说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我游历了很多地方。”他接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后，我找到了去埃及的路。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说那是一个很棒的地方！”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我的孩子，它是很棒的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是随着时间的流逝，我变老了也想念我自己的国家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想在我死之前再看一看我的弟弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我回家来找他。但是我太晚了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能违背上帝的旨意。”泽巴说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来，可怜的人，再多吃一点吧！这样会让你好过一些。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布又吃了一些大盘子里的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经得到了安慰。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虽然我的弟弟已经去世了，但是他还一直活在阿拉丁这个孩子身上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布把手放在阿拉丁的肩上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“侄子，你是这个家的一家之主了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你学会了做什么工作呢？你要怎么照顾你这个优秀的妈妈呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁感到很愧疚，他看着自己的妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他什么都没学会。”妈妈生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么都没有。每天，他都在街上玩儿游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的爸爸因为他不想工作伤心而死。”她哭了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我白天夜晚都在工作，照顾这个懒惰的孩子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁羞愧地低下了头，但是魔法师微笑着安慰那位寡妇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“困难都已经过去了。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上帝赐予了我财富，我可以帮助你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁高兴地抬起了头，他的妈妈擦去了眼泪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的侄子，你必须学会做一项事业。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你妈妈在辛勤劳作的时候你却每天都在玩耍是一件让人脸红的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对，伯父。”阿拉丁小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子，现在别担心了。”马格里布拍了拍阿拉丁的肩膀说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会给你买一间装满物品的商店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样你就可以成为一名商人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>买东西，卖东西，然后变成有钱人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一名商人？”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“变成有钱人？”他的妈妈也问了一句。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拍了拍手，抱着她的儿子，在他耳边小声说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个男人一定是你真正的伯父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我吃够了，现在已经晚了。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>354704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我明天早上会回来，我们一起去集市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>361514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>371698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要给阿拉丁买成为一个年轻商人需要的所有东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>